# Copy to `.dev.vars` for local dev; set the same names in prod with `wrangler secret put <NAME>`.
# Stripe secret key + webhook signing secret (NEVER commit real values):
STRIPE_API_KEY=sk_test_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
# Note: STRIPE_PRICE_ID is a non-secret var set in wrangler.jsonc (replace YOUR_STRIPE_PRICE_ID).
